msgstr "Talk_Odosu"

msgctxt "112_Saejima"
msgid "For a buncha men in suits, this don't look too gentlemanly."
msgstr "Para tratarse de un grupo de trajeados, esto no parece muy caballeroso."

msgctxt "124_Femme Fatale"
msgid "Please, help me!"
msgstr "¡Por favor, ayudame!"

msgctxt "184_Suited Goon"
msgid "Not so fast."
msgstr "No tan rapido."

msgctxt "208_Suited Goon"
msgid "You? I thought I told you to get lost!"
msgstr "¿Y tú? ¡Ya te dicho que te perdieras!"

msgctxt "220_Saejima"
msgid "It's clear as a kappa you're up to some shady shit..."
msgstr "Está claro como el agua que aquí hay algo turbio..."

msgctxt "232_Suited Goon"
msgid "Which isn't your problem, so beat it already!"
msgstr "¡Eso no es problema tuyo, así que lárgate de una vez!"

msgctxt "244_Saejima"
msgid "When someone asks me for help, it becomes my problem.\\r\n"\n"'Specially when they're surrounded by a buncha suits."
msgstr "Cuando alguien me pide ayuda, eso ya es mi problema.\\r\n"\n"Especialmente cuando esta rodeada de un montón de trajeados."

msgctxt "256_Suited Goon"
msgid "Great, we've got us a wannabe hero..."
msgstr "Vaya, conque tenemos un héroe aquí..."

msgctxt "268_Suited Henchman"
msgid "Look, this is one damsel in distress you don't wanna save.\\r\n"\n"Meddle in our business and there will be real consequences."
msgstr "Mira, no querrás salvar a esta \"damisela en apuros\".\\r\n"\n"Metete en tus propios asuntos y no habrá problemas."

msgctxt "280_Saejima"
msgid "That a threat?"
msgstr "¿Es eso una amenaza?"

msgctxt "292_Suited Henchman"
msgid "No, it's a promise. Playing hero for some woman you've never even met will get you killed."
msgstr "No, es una promesa. Jugar a ser el héroe con mujeres que no conoces te va a costar la vida."

msgctxt "304_Saejima"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "316_Suited Goon"
msgid "Hey, dumbass! Hello in there!"
msgstr "¡Tierra a imbecil! ¿¡Nos escuchas!?"

msgctxt "328_Suited Henchman"
msgid "I guess you're ignoring my warning."
msgstr "Supongo que no te importa tu vida."

msgctxt "340_Saejima"
msgid "Guess I am."
msgstr "Supongo."

msgctxt "352_Suited Henchman"
msgid "Then you've painted us into a corner. Try not to get your blood on my suit!"
msgstr "Entonces complicaste las cosas. ¡Procura no manchar mi traje con tu sangre!"

